# Semgrep ignore patterns for navigation2
# This file specifies paths and patterns to exclude from semgrep scanning

# Exclude all test directories
**/test/
**/tests/

# Exclude build and install directories
**/build/
**/install/
**/devel/

# Exclude git and CI/CD configuration directories
.git/
.github/
.circleci/
.devcontainer/

# Exclude documentation directories
**/doc/
**/docs/

# Exclude third-party and external code
**/third_party/
**/external/

# Exclude generated files and build artifacts
**/*.o
**/*.so
**/*.a
**/CMakeFiles/
